{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/use-a-span-to-target-inline-elements","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi span za ciljanje inline elemenata","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete koristiti spanove za kreiranje inline elemenata. Zapamtite kada smo koristili klasu <code>btn-block</code> da bismo učinili dugme koje popunjava cijeli red?</p>\n<p><button class='btn' style='background-color: rgb(0, 100, 0);  color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>normal button</button></p>\n<p><button class='btn btn-block' style='background-color: rgb(0, 100, 0);  color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>btn-block button</button></p>\n<p>Ovo pokazuje razliku između 'inline' i 'block' elemenata.</p>\n<p>Koristeći inline element <code>span</code>, možete postaviti više elemenata u jednom redu, pa čak i stilizovati različite dijelove tog reda na različite načine.</p>\n<p>Uzimajući element <code>span</code>, umotajte riječ <code>love</code> unutar elementa <code>p</code> koji trenutno sadrži tekst <code>Things cats love</code>. Zatim dodijelite <code>span</code>-u klasu <code>text-danger</code> kako biste učinili tekst crvenim.</p>\n<p>Evo kako to raditi za element <code>p</code> koji sadrži tekst <code>Top 3 things cats hate</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;p>Top 3 things cats &#x3C;span class=\"text-danger\">hate:&#x3C;/span>&#x3C;/p>\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aedf08845","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18370,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/use-a-span-to-target-inline-elements"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\r\n<style>\r\n\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: Lobster, Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .thick-green-border {\r\n    border-color: green;\r\n    border-width: 10px;\r\n    border-style: solid;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"text-primary text-center\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\r\n\r\n  <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"img-responsive thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\r\n\r\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Tuxedo cats running on dirt ground.\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-primary\">Like</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-info\">Info</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-danger\">Delete</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <p>Things cats love:</p>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>catnip</li>\r\n    <li>laser pointers</li>\r\n    <li>lasagna</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li>flea treatment</li>\r\n    <li>thunder</li>\r\n    <li>other cats</li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Indoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Loving</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Crazy</label>\r\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\r\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\r\n  </form>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>span</code> element treba da bude unutar vašeg <code>p</code> elementa.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('p span'),1);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>span</code> element bi trebalo da sadrži samo tekst <code>love</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(document.querySelector('p span')?.textContent,/love/i);\r\nassert.notMatch(document.querySelector('p span')?.textContent, /Things cats/i);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>span</code> element treba da ima klasu <code>text-danger</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('span')?.classList?.contains('text-danger'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>span</code> element bi trebalo da imati zatvarajući tag.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/<\\/span>/g);\r\nassert.match(code,/<span/g);\r\nassert.equal(code.match(/<\\/span>/g).length,code.match(/<span/g).length);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#bootstrap","dashedName":"use-a-span-to-target-inline-elements","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"bootstrap","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/create-a-custom-heading","prevChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/ditch-custom-css-for-bootstrap","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aedf08845","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challeng